    Parent updateParentAddChild(ParentTo to, @MappingTarget Parent parent);

    default List&lt;Child&gt; updateChildrenList(ParentTo to, Parent parent) {

        //add here your custom mapping implementation

    }

If you need, there is also a CollectionMappingStrategy called ADDER_PREFERRED that can be applied to override the default behaviour.

